        <div n="949A14W2">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-949A14W2-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-949A14W2-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-949A14W2-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">FROM THE FRENCH.<ref target="#spp-949A14W2-footnote-headnote-1">1</ref><note n="1" xml:id="spp-949A14W2-footnote-headnote-1" place="foot">A French gentleman dining with some company on a fast-day, called for some bacon and eggs. The rest were very angry, and reproved him for so heinous a sin; whereupon he wrote the following lines, which are translated above;<lb/><lb/>Peut on croire avec bon sens<lb/><lb/><lb/>Qu'un lardon le mit en colère,<lb/><lb/>Ou, que manger un hareng,<lb/><lb/><lb/>C'est un secret pour lui plaire?<lb/><lb/>En sa glorie envelopé,<lb/><lb/>Songe-t-il bien de nos soupés?── H</note></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-949A14W2-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-949A14W2-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-949A14W2-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-949A14W2-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-949A14W2-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-949A14W2-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-949A14W2-line-1" n="1">&lt;Peut on croire avec bon sens</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-949A14W2-line-2" n="2">&lt;Qu'un lardon le mit en colère,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A14W2-line-3" n="3">&lt;Ou, que manger un hareng,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-949A14W2-line-4" n="4">&lt;C'est un secret pour lui plaire?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A14W2-line-5" n="5">&lt;En sa glorie envelopé,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A14W2-line-6" n="6">&lt;Songe-t-il bien de nos soupés?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A14W2-line-7" n="7">W<hi rend="small-caps">HO</hi> can believe with common sense,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A14W2-line-8" n="8">A bacon slice gives God offence;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A14W2-line-9" n="9">Or, how a herring has a charm</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A14W2-line-10" n="10">Almighty vengeance to disarm?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A14W2-line-11" n="11">Wrapp'd up in majesty divine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-949A14W2-line-12" n="12">Does he regard on what we dine?</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
